data.description: Nestled in the heart of the vibrant 55-and-up community of Sun City Center, 1611 Cloister Drive is a haven of comfort and convenience. This delightful property features 2 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, two living areas, a dining room, an open floor plan, and a sunroom, all thoughtfully designed to enhance your Florida living experience.The kitchen is a standout, boasting beautiful granite countertops that seamlessly blend aesthetics with functionality. Whether you're a culinary enthusiast or prefer quick, easy meals, this kitchen is up to the task.Two spacious bedrooms provide ample rest and relaxation space, and two well-appointed bathrooms ensure privacy and comfort. The sunroom is a highlight, offering a perfect spot to savor the Florida sunshine year-round, be it with a morning coffee or an evening book.    One of the biggest draws of this property is the impressive array of community amenities. Sun City Center residents enjoy access to a top-notch clubhouse, inviting pools (including a unique walking pool), a relaxing spa, a well-equipped fitness center, tennis courts, and racquetball facilities. It's the ideal environment for staying active and socializing with your neighbors.Situated in a prime location within the Sun City Center community, 1611 Cloister Drive offers the convenience of easy access to all the amenities and services that make life in this community so vibrant and fulfilling. It's also a golf cart community, making it a breeze to explore the neighborhood and its numerous offerings.    This property is move-in ready, waiting for you to experience the endless possibilities it offers in the heart of this thriving 55+ community. Don't miss your chance to make this piece of Sun City Center yours. Contact us today to arrange a tour and discover the exceptional lifestyle that 1611 Cloister Drive provides.
